name: dreamling's swing
description:
lucid swing for meditative encoding, trancing and journeying in one's mind created for you by CROSSLUCID.

HD video loop presenting a GAN-generated and later VR-sculpted symbol. a pendulum of everlasting transformation unfolding to a sonic landscape potent for daydreaming.

each a full edition is sold, a new piece of the evolving audiovisual string is released. collect a few and create your own daydream.

we are a hybrid collective prototyping experiences and tools for emerging futures through world-building, film, CGI, AI and collage.
